plot: When Toby and Michelle go after a suspect in the murder of a Latin crime boss, interference from a police superintendent halts their case.

A parking garage meeting between two men ends with one dead by gunshot. As IIB investigates its connection with falsified passports, a roadblock emerges in the form of Superintendent Nichola Martrell, who suspends Alvin Klein and redirects the team down blind allies. Someone's feeding her bad intel, and the investigation tiptoes very carefully around her to turn up an undercover agent and his set-up to bring down two crime factions in an internecine meeting.—statmanjeff
